entry.title: New release for Scratch Map: 1.1.12
entry.content:
Preparing to make some updates! Regenerating 1.1.12 at previous state (no changes) and triggered push to docker.io and ghcr.io

What's Changed

  • Update Docs, Add Australian Map by @ad3m3r5 in https://github.com/ad3m3r5/scratch-map/pull/13
  • Add French map by @ad3m3r5 in https://github.com/ad3m3r5/scratch-map/pull/14
  • Add Mexican Map by @ad3m3r5 in https://github.com/ad3m3r5/scratch-map/pull/15
  • Updated pages and docs, added maps by @ad3m3r5 in https://github.com/ad3m3r5/scratch-map/pull/16
  • Add german map by @ad3m3r5 in https://github.com/ad3m3r5/scratch-map/pull/17
  • Update Docs, Add Maps by @ad3m3r5 in https://github.com/ad3m3r5/scratch-map/pull/18

Full Changelog: https://github.com/ad3m3r5/scratch-map/compare/1.1.11...1.1.12
